 compliant  light directiondetermines where the light is mostly directed ambient lighting means that the light is not focused in any one direction up  down lighting fixtures direct light in both the up and downward position up or down fixtures have the option of being mounted in either the up or down position bath bar fixtures are sometimes called vanity strip lights and do not point up or down but rather illuminates out in all directions please see examples below light direction ambient lighting  down lighting  up  down lighting  adjustable lighting  up lighting  number of bulbstotal number of bulbs that this fixture uses number of bulbs                   bulb typedetermines the type of bulb used with this fixture incandescent bulbs are the most common but the most inefficient fluorescent and led bulbs are most efficient while halogen and xenon provide the best color rendering bulb type incandescent  led  compact fluorescent  xenon  krypton  halogen  fluorescent  bulb base medium e  g  integrated led  candelabra e  bi pin  mini candelabra e  gu  gu  fluorescent pin  gy  cfl plugin  gu  medium e  specialty    chandelier type linear  mini  abstract  candle style  drum  shaded  sputnik    pendant type single pendant  multi light  linear  pendant size mini under  inches  medium  inches  large over  inches  sconce type plug in  ambient sconce  upward arm  flush mount  wall washer  wallchiere  multi light    extension  inches or less   to  inches   to  inches  heightthe measurement from the very bottom of the fixture to the top does not measure chain or stems for ceiling hung fixtures height  to  inches   to  inches   to  inches   to  inches   to  inches   to  inches   to  inches   to  inches    widthwidth is the measured distance in inches from front to back width  to  inches   to  inches   to  inches   to  inches   to  inches  styleto help match existing decor we have determined what we feel to be the best style for this fixture please see below for examples of our mos